<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="root-v">root <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ruːt/    美 /ruːt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 生根；(使) 扎根：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Great cause <strong>is rooted in</strong> great dreams, so as well the great life. 
伟大的事业源于伟大的梦想；伟大的人生源于伟大的梦境。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With mother’s words <strong>deeply rooted in</strong> my soul, I never doubted we would succeed. 
母亲的话深深地根植于我的灵魂，我坚信我们一定会成功。</p></div></div>